Mom, I thought you said
10 more minutes.

00:27.628 --> 00:31.463
That was 20 minutes ago.
Upstairs. Now.

00:31.465 --> 00:33.799
I hate you.

00:33.801 --> 00:36.235
- And no playing on your phone!
- Ugh!

00:36.237 --> 00:38.437
