00:53.988 --> 00:56.021
Gabriel...

00:56.023 --> 00:57.523
you know why it's important

00:57.525 --> 00:59.625
to listen to your mother,
don't you?

01:01.295 --> 01:04.430
Because if you don't,
the Cucuy will get you.

01:04.432 --> 01:06.465
The what?

01:06.467 --> 01:09.868
You mean your mother never
told you about the Cucuy?

01:09.870 --> 01:11.203
Uh-uh.

01:11.205 --> 01:12.237
Ah.

01:14.308 --> 01:19.011
They say that he goes
from house to house every night,

01:19.013 --> 01:22.448
looking for children
who have misbehaved.

01:22.450 --> 01:25.684
And when he finds them,
he hides,

01:25.686 --> 01:28.987
waiting till they're all alone.

01:28.989 --> 01:34.126
In fact, he could
be here right now.

01:35.396 --> 01:38.030
Maybe he's hiding
under your bed.

01:38.032 --> 01:40.999
Or maybe...

01:41.001 --> 01:43.836
he's in the closet.

01:43.838 --> 01:46.538
He comes out
when you're sleeping.

01:46.540 --> 01:50.442
He puts you in his sack
and takes you to his cave...

01:53.047 --> 01:56.215
where he eats you.

01:56.217 --> 01:58.016
What are you talking about
in here?

01:58.018 --> 02:01.386
Oh,<i> mijito</i> and I
were just talking about

02:01.388 --> 02:04.256
how important it is for children
to listen to their parents.

02:04.258 --> 02:05.524
- Weren't we,<i> mijito?</i>
- Yes.

02:05.526 --> 02:06.859
Yes.

02:06.861 --> 02:09.061
- Ready to go, Mama?
- Yes.

02:09.062 --> 02:11.497
Do you have to go?

02:11.499 --> 02:14.366
Someone has to take
your <i> abuelita</i> home.

02:16.270 --> 02:19.171
Don't worry, you'll be fine.

02:27.081 --> 02:29.381
Javi, we're leaving now.

02:43.297 --> 02:44.429
Javi?

03:30.945 --> 03:31.977
Javi!

03:31.979 --> 03:33.579
Man!

03:33.581 --> 03:35.948
You gotta stop believing
that crap Grandma reads you.

03:35.950 --> 03:37.816
You jerk!

03:39.153 --> 03:41.486
Oh, that's too good.

03:42.957 --> 03:45.924
<i>Oh, my God!</i>

03:45.926 --> 03:48.026
<i>Javi!</i>

03:48.028 --> 03:49.661
Oh, this is priceless.

03:49.663 --> 03:50.729
<i>Javi!</i>

04:03.444 --> 04:05.043
Gabe?

04:23.297 --> 04:26.164
Javi, what are you doing?

04:29.336 --> 04:30.902
There's someone out there.

04:30.904 --> 04:32.204
Where?

04:35.542 --> 04:36.875
There was.

04:36.877 --> 04:39.311
Just leave me alone.

05:26.894 --> 05:28.894
Javi, what's going on?
I'm scared!

05:28.896 --> 05:30.962
- Hide now!
- Okay.

05:40.974 --> 05:42.174
Shh.

06:06.166 --> 06:09.201
Oh, my God!

06:26.420 --> 06:29.287
Javi?

06:29.289 --> 06:31.289
Javi?

06:31.291 --> 06:33.525
Javi!

07:11.799 --> 07:13.899
There she is.

07:13.901 --> 07:15.233
Gross.

07:15.235 --> 07:17.602
She can't even hear us.

07:23.343 --> 07:25.844
Smelly Melly.

07:35.155 --> 07:36.855
- Hey!
- What's the matter?

07:36.857 --> 07:38.690
- You can't hear without this?
- Give it back!

07:38.692 --> 07:40.926
Hey, can you hear this?

07:42.930 --> 07:44.496
Here.

07:44.498 --> 07:47.833
If you want this,
you gotta catch us.

07:47.835 --> 07:49.601
Come on, let's go! Go!

07:55.375 --> 07:57.676
Stop! Please! Wait!

07:57.678 --> 08:00.245
Go, go, go!

08:00.247 --> 08:01.446
Crap.

08:04.284 --> 08:05.617
Move!

08:07.855 --> 08:08.920
Please!

08:08.922 --> 08:10.455
Later, loser!

08:12.426 --> 08:13.992
Adios!

08:17.231 --> 08:19.464
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

08:19.466 --> 08:20.966
Well, if it isn't
the big sister.

08:20.968 --> 08:22.400
I told you,
leave her alone!

08:22.402 --> 08:23.768
Sofie!

08:23.770 --> 08:26.438
It's not my fault
she's a reject!

08:26.440 --> 08:27.539
Ooh!

08:27.541 --> 08:28.540
Stop! Hey, stop!

08:33.413 --> 08:35.046
- Stop resisting!
- Come on!

08:35.048 --> 08:36.982
Didn't you see
what they were doing to her?

08:36.984 --> 08:38.850
Let me go!

08:59.339 --> 09:00.772
What the hell is going on?

09:00.774 --> 09:02.908
I told him it was an accident!

09:02.910 --> 09:04.943
Your daughter assaulted
a police officer.

09:04.945 --> 09:07.112
I was trying
to protect Amelia, Mom.

09:07.114 --> 09:11.016
He just came up behind me.
I didn't know it was a cop.

09:12.686 --> 09:15.220
Come with me, please.

09:19.092 --> 09:22.827
Take them down to my office.
Be right there.

09:23.997 --> 09:26.798
Think you have problems, Sofia?

09:26.800 --> 09:28.433
Think about that poor family.

09:28.435 --> 09:30.702
There has to be
something that you can do.

09:30.704 --> 09:32.370
She's your niece,
for Christ's sakes!

09:32.372 --> 09:34.706
It's a felony, Rebecca.
There are regulations to follow.

09:34.708 --> 09:37.242
Regulations?
And this is how you do it?

09:39.813 --> 09:42.347
Sofia Alondra Martin.

09:42.349 --> 09:44.015
As your attorney has advised,

09:44.017 --> 09:46.651
this charge carries a minimum
sentence of six months

09:46.653 --> 09:48.853
in a juvenile detention center.

09:50.524 --> 09:52.724
In light of your father's death

09:52.726 --> 09:55.694
and other extenuating
circumstances,

09:55.696 --> 09:59.497
I'm sentencing you
to six months of house arrest.

09:59.499 --> 10:01.666
You will wear an ankle monitor,

10:01.668 --> 10:04.502
and you will not be allowed
to leave the premises

10:04.504 --> 10:07.472
without expressed permission.

10:07.474 --> 10:09.975
Ms. Martin,
I strongly urge you

10:09.977 --> 10:13.311
to consider the leniency
you've been shown here today.

10:13.313 --> 10:18.216
And I assure you, young lady,
it will not happen again.

10:18.218 --> 10:19.851
Am I clear?

10:19.853 --> 10:22.520
Yes, Your Honor.

10:22.522 --> 10:25.090
This court is adjourned.

10:29.696 --> 10:32.430
You know that I'm picking up
extra shifts at the hotel

10:32.432 --> 10:34.432
