have done it.

15:32.365 --> 15:35.500
Jesse just texted me.

15:35.502 --> 15:39.871
Okay, first of all,
we've only kissed like once.

15:39.873 --> 15:41.372
No, he's not coming over.

15:41.374 --> 15:44.409
My parents are gonna be home
in like an hour.

15:52.852 --> 15:55.553
I'm gonna call you back,
all right?

15:55.555 --> 15:57.021
Okay, bye.

