18:51.431 --> 18:53.931
<i>Already reeling
from a suicide last year,</i>

18:53.933 --> 18:55.700
<i>the small-town
junior high school</i>

18:55.702 --> 18:57.235
<i>is now desperately searching
for the two students</i>

18:57.237 --> 18:58.936
<i>who have been abducted.</i>

18:58.938 --> 19:01.906
<i>Starting tonight,
there will be a 7:00 curfew.</i>

19:01.908 --> 19:04.542
Hey, guys, finish up.
We're gonna be late.

19:06.379 --> 19:09.881
They didn't do all that
for Javier.

19:14.587 --> 19:18.422
Those posts I saw online
last night,

19:18.424 --> 19:20.992
that was her, wasn't it?

20:07.774 --> 20:09.707
What's he doing?

20:13.513 --> 20:16.214
Keeping someone down there?

20:58.491 --> 21:00.791
You scared the hell out of me!

21:00.793 --> 21:04.862
Are you, uh,
watching that house?

21:04.864 --> 21:07.331
- I...
- I get it.

21:07.333 --> 21:09.734
Creepy guy, creepy house.

21:09.736 --> 21:11.502
No, no, it's not
what you think.

21:11.504 --> 21:13.337
Oh, so you weren't
watching him.

21:14.974 --> 21:17.008
Let me show you something.

21:17.010 --> 21:18.876
Follow me.

21:22.548 --> 21:25.249
Is this really
what the judge had in mind

21:25.251 --> 21:27.151
when he gave you
house arrest?

21:27.153 --> 21:29.720
You don't think it's weird?
Those two kids disappeared

21:29.722 --> 21:32.089
right around the time
this guy moves in.

21:32.091 --> 21:35.059
You think he did it?

21:35.061 --> 21:36.761
Yeah, or he's involved.

21:36.763 --> 21:37.928
Because he bought chains?

21:37.930 --> 21:39.230
And lye.

21:39.232 --> 21:41.232
Well, maybe he's making soap.

21:41.234 --> 21:42.733
Okay.

21:42.735 --> 21:44.835
Have you been watching
the whole neighborhood

21:44.837 --> 21:46.203
from in here?

21:47.273 --> 21:48.372
You ever watch me?

21:48.374 --> 21:51.909
No, no, of course not.

21:51.911 --> 21:54.245
I mean,
not like specifically.

21:54.247 --> 21:56.947
You are such a liar.

21:56.949 --> 21:59.383
- Okay.
- What have you seen?

21:59.385 --> 22:00.918
Like I said,

22:00.920 --> 22:05.623
