of watching you.

22:06.926 --> 22:08.726
Uh-huh.

22:12.565 --> 22:14.198
How's your hand?

22:14.200 --> 22:16.567
It's-- It's fine.

22:18.938 --> 22:20.705
Remember back in fourth grade?

22:20.707 --> 22:21.706
Mm-hmm.

22:21.708 --> 22:23.874
In Ms. Fiorello's class.

22:23.876 --> 22:25.710
You got stung by that bee.

22:25.712 --> 22:28.879
First of all,
it was a hornet.

22:28.881 --> 22:31.782
Second of all,
it really hurt, so...

22:31.784 --> 22:33.484
Uh-oh.

22:33.486 --> 22:35.586
What? What?

22:35.588 --> 22:37.655
It looks infected.

22:37.657 --> 22:39.623
We're definitely gonna
have to amputate.

22:39.625 --> 22:41.225
- Hey!
- Where's that hacksaw?

22:41.227 --> 22:42.326
Shut up!

22:44.764 --> 22:48.766
You know, if you're gonna keep
peeking through my window,

22:48.768 --> 22:50.968
the least I could do is,
I don't know,

22:50.970 --> 22:53.504
text you when I'm doing
something worth watching.

22:53.506 --> 22:55.639
Oh, how considerate.

22:55.641 --> 22:57.308
Put in your number.

22:58.478 --> 23:00.077
Are all the boys
at St. Stephen's

23:00.079 --> 23:01.812
this chivalrous?

23:01.814 --> 23:05.816
Maybe when you get parole,
you could come and find out.

23:05.818 --> 23:07.051
Cute.

23:08.454 --> 23:10.654
