23:46.492 --> 23:48.759
Screw it.

23:48.761 --> 23:51.095
I got three minutes.

23:51.097 --> 23:53.364
Okay, let's do this.

24:18.458 --> 24:20.357
Sierra.

24:20.359 --> 24:23.160
Um, I think you're confused.

24:52.124 --> 24:54.225
Get out of here.
Get out of here.

24:54.227 --> 24:56.293
What the hell
are you doing here?

24:56.295 --> 24:57.695
I thought you were
under house arrest.

24:57.697 --> 24:58.896
I don't want any trouble.

24:58.898 --> 25:00.197
You don't want any trouble?

25:00.199 --> 25:01.532
You should've thought about that

25:01.534 --> 25:03.067
before you hit my boy
with your car.

25:04.670 --> 25:06.170
Oh, you got an important date?

25:06.172 --> 25:08.873
Look, I just need
to get back, okay? Please.

25:08.875 --> 25:11.909
Unfortunately, your uncle isn't
bailing you out this time.

25:11.911 --> 25:13.277
Just back off!

25:15.515 --> 25:18.415
Oh, looks like your time
is running out.

25:18.417 --> 25:19.783
Tick tock, bitch.

26:27.553 --> 26:29.253
<i>Attention.</i>

26:29.255 --> 26:32.222
<i>Starting tonight,
there is a curfew of 7 p.m.</i>

26:32.224 --> 26:34.992
<i>for all residents
under the age of 18.</i>

26:34.994 --> 26:37.394
<i>All residents
under the age of 18</i>

26:37.396 --> 26:39.229
<i>are required to be
back in their homes.</i>

26:39.231 --> 26:40.931
Come on,
we can get in the back.

26:40.933 --> 26:43.834
<i>Again, 7 p.m.
for all residents...</i>

26:48.140 --> 26:49.373
Hey.

26:51.310 --> 26:53.978
- You guys remember her?
- Remember her?

26:53.980 --> 26:56.680
Can't believe it's already been
a year since she killed herself.

26:56.682 --> 26:57.982
Classic.

26:57.984 --> 26:59.550
Rest in peace.

27:33.619 --> 27:35.486
Someone there?

27:50.002 --> 27:51.201
What the hell?

28:05.851 --> 28:07.117
Hello?

28:38.250 --> 28:40.384
Guys, guys, we gotta go now!

28:40.386 --> 28:42.119
Guys, we gotta go right now!

28:42.121 --> 28:44.922
We gotta go! Dude, dude!
We gotta go right now!

28:44.924 --> 28:46.757
