- There's something else here.

28:46.759 --> 28:50.060
I saw it downstairs.
Please, we gotta go, please!

29:15.154 --> 29:17.287
<i>Malo.</i>

29:20.459 --> 29:23.327
No, please, no!
No! No!

29:23.329 --> 29:27.898
No, no, no, no!
Please, please, no!

29:27.900 --> 29:28.932
No!

30:56.956 --> 30:58.255
He's coming for you.

31:12.037 --> 31:14.771
As some of you
might have already heard,

31:14.773 --> 31:18.141
last night, 16-year-old
Travis Baines disappeared

31:18.143 --> 31:21.778
from the vicinity of
Glimmer Peak Junior High School.

31:21.780 --> 31:24.014
Chief Martin, what are you
doing to find these children?

31:24.016 --> 31:25.549
What are you doing
to find my boy?

31:25.551 --> 31:27.050
