goes to school here!

31:32.524 --> 31:34.524
Is it true they all went
to the same school?

31:34.526 --> 31:37.294
This have anything to do
with Teresa Fuentes' suicide?

31:37.296 --> 31:39.630
Yeah, we wanna know
what you're doing!

31:39.632 --> 31:43.734
Look, as of now, last night
we instituted a curfew,

31:43.736 --> 31:46.403
which will be continuing
for the foreseeable future.

31:46.405 --> 31:49.339
Does Glimmer Peak
have a serial killer?

31:49.341 --> 31:50.874
It's still an ongoing case,

31:50.876 --> 31:53.210
so I'm not gonna discuss
specifics at this time.

31:53.212 --> 31:55.012
Chief!

31:55.014 --> 31:56.713
What about the Cucuy?

31:56.715 --> 31:58.315
I'm sorry, the what?

31:58.317 --> 32:00.017
El Cucuy.

32:00.019 --> 32:02.052
Comes in the middle
of the night.

32:02.054 --> 32:04.154
Take away youngsters
that won't listen.

32:04.156 --> 32:06.690
Keeps them for a while,
fattens them up,

32:06.692 --> 32:08.992
eats them, body and soul.

32:08.994 --> 32:10.661
You better get yourself
a nice <i> abuelita,</i> Chief.

32:12.564 --> 32:15.165
Shut up!
This is serious!

32:15.167 --> 32:17.834
Look, all I can
say is of now that my department

32:17.836 --> 32:19.236
is doing everything
we can to make sure

32:19.238 --> 32:20.938
these horrific events
come to a close

32:20.940 --> 32:24.007
as quickly
and safely as possible.

32:24.009 --> 32:25.375
Next question?

32:25.377 --> 32:27.945
<i>- Si!</i>
