32:50.803 --> 32:54.604
I was, um, tagging.

32:54.606 --> 32:56.039
Mostly lockers.

32:56.041 --> 32:57.941
You saw Travis again?

32:57.943 --> 32:59.643
Yeah, he came back.

32:59.645 --> 33:02.946
He looked kinda,
